{"tid":1570070,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「重開」藍絲又追擊港台！一人一信表揚港台","createTime":"2019-09-15T01:33:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-16T15:35:52.000Z","uid":220977,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"d8bca09c7220502d421432afebcb46f4da101958","tid":1570070,"uid":220977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T01:33:56.000Z","msg":"救命呀！繼之前香港政研發起萬人包圍港台，誣蔑港台偏幫示威者，hkgpao又搞左個聯署搞港台<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSeiWLHx7Ao-IsJrBjFq1xNtLjCnPHXWyoSAJqmaTmHdZMN32w/viewform\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSeiWLHx7Ao-IsJrBjFq1xNtLjCnPHXWyoSAJqmaTmHdZMN32w%2Fviewform&d=xWOcOck8MQRdM6xM79L4mGVlCuV5KOpEhASsqV1EMe4%3D&h=1a0d129b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSeiWLHx7Ao-IsJrBjFq1xNtLjCnPHXWyoSAJqmaTmHdZMN32w/viewform</a><br />\n<br />\n唔該大家幫手拉到最低report呢個google form - 檢舉濫用情形 &mdash;&gt; 煽動仇恨、暴力或違法/無禮行為<br />\n<br />\n====================================<br />\n<br />\n我真係好嬲呀，港台係一個公正持平既傳媒黎架嗎，我地要還港台一個公道!<br />\n<br />\n之前原由柏実巴打提議 - 我地不如一人一信去通訊局表揚港台一直用不偏不倚,專業,用心既態度製作節目，多謝佢地謹守崗位，堅持報道真相！<br />\n<br />\n通訊局得投訴電郵無表揚電郵<br />\n依個係佢地有關廣播事務既聯絡電郵:      webmaster@ofca.gov.hk<br />\n<br />\n亦可以send埋俾港台：<br />\n香港電台機構傳訊組: ccu@rthk.hk<br />\n<br />\n內容記得講明睇開港台31 定32台，最like咩節目同點解<br />\n<br />\n麻煩大家寫返自己嘅意見出嚟，短短地都得㗎啦，唔需要好文筆，一模一樣既信有機會俾佢地當做同一封信！港台咁多好節目唔會太難寫！唔該唔好寫到佢地偏幫示威者咁。佢地唔係呀！佢地只係報道緊真相<br />\n<br />\n呢個未必係最好既方法，大家有橋請提議！<br />\n<br />\n最後最重要都係大家長開31，32台，下載晒佢地d apps, 提曬佢地既youtube片<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f1a90680cb24640a72914a91053790fc04d3c1b","tid":1570070,"uid":220977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T01:34:42.000Z","msg":"幫幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f44c4b2869f1cace1cea1eb106ab6ff38b11244","tid":1570070,"uid":220977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T01:34:52.000Z","msg":"我愛港台"},{"pid":"ae5f59f804405c2b79b40a485275897959f110f8","tid":1570070,"uid":220977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T01:35:04.000Z","msg":"自推十下"},{"pid":"b15f82ef8e5b4c03772ed2c177ee956da76962e3","tid":1570070,"uid":220977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T01:35:17.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"ff4d1b86be345b7bf55056ab8a9d199b470727bf","tid":1570070,"uid":208452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T01:35:23.000Z","msg":"有野想捐可以FB搵我地香港自由之書阿<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n[澄清]國難五金課金問題&mdash;照舊課！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1521564/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1521564/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n國難五金專訪 [開鋪事直請留意國難五金FB]<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1521301/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1521301/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n【眾籌】 已集合超過1000名巴絲感想 香港編年史<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1379634/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1379634/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\nFB: 國難五金, 香港自由之書"},{"pid":"212bad72960189431c98cd15139ecee27b7c989e","tid":1570070,"uid":220977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T01:35:31.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"57f0e94cbbd8fddd233afcb7112b665431b2df3e","tid":1570070,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T01:36:05.000Z","msg":"得一個選項既投票"},{"pid":"d0845161e404bd001b5d6ff86de65e8b